[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man in hospital after 'targeted' shooting in Stepps

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 42-year-old man is being treated in hospital after being shot in a targeted attack near Glasgow.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police were called to Honeywell Drive, in Stepps, just after 21:00 on Sunday.
The man is said to be in a stable condition in hospital.
